# GitHub Repositories Viewer

## Instructions

### 1.Open `index.html` in a Browser

Open the `index.html` file in your preferred web browser. You can do this by either double-clicking the file or using your browser's "Open File" option.

## Live Demo

link to hosted web app :(https://lucky-queijadas-c1bd2d.netlify.app/#)

## Additional Information

- Ensure that your internet connection is active to fetch data from the GitHub API.
- A loader will be displayed while fetching data to keep you informed about the ongoing process.
- Feel free to use the hosted web app or run the project locally to meet your preferences.

Contributions to enhance and customize the project are always welcome!
